    public static enum Descriptor.Supports
extends java.lang.Enum<Descriptor.Supports>
    Defines the capability of the algorithm. It is possible that the list will be extended to the complete list of ImageJ's PlugInFilter Flags
    See Also:
    PlugInFilter, Descriptor.supports()
